---
title: Double Slow-Cooked Steak & Mushroom Pie with Mash Potato & Panko Topping
description: There’s no need for dinner to be rushed, sometimes it’s nice to take your time and enjoy as your kitchen fills with the aromas of a golden oven-baked pie. The extra time allows the hearty mushrooms, beef and rich sauce to come together for a mouth-watering filling. So, sit back, relax and enjoy.
